               <item n="m_philcomment_old">&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;b4.&lt;/b&gt; The &lt;i&gt;nt&lt;/i&gt;-participle &lt;i&gt;yänmāṣṣeñcaṃ&lt;/i&gt; shows the late form of the nominative plural ending instead of standard &lt;i&gt;-añ&lt;/i&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;b5.&lt;/b&gt; The form &lt;i&gt;(ta)nmaṣṣitär&lt;/i&gt; is 3sg middle of the Kausativ of the root &lt;i&gt;täm-&lt;/i&gt; 'to produce', cf. [[Malzahn 2010]]: 653.&lt;/p&gt;   
